description: If your stomach is rumbling for something real tasty in Columbus, you better run over to Mya’s Fried Chicken because their signature dishes are famously delicious. At Mya’s, you’ll find truck-made biscuits and fried chicken sliders with herbed honey drizzle, smashed potatoes with pan gravy, chicken and waffles, and so much more that will get your mouth watering. Come on out to this truck soon and order yourself some of Columbus’ best grub.
name: Mya's Fried Chicken
